## Objective
Create frontend service methods to fetch sprints and tasks from the backend API.

## Requirements
- Add methods to the existing API client (e.g. `client/src/services/api.ts` or similar) to call GET `/api/instances/:id/sprints`.
- Ensure the methods are strongly typed according to the shared types.
- Provide proper error handling for failed requests.
